      "term_name": "Grail",
      "term_slug": "grail"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n262\nNeeds Review\n262\n348 It is an experienced psyche, not new + pristine but dedicated + shrewd (withough limited). It is not \"like a little child,\" as the B psyche was 2000 years ago; it provides an enormous back log of practical experience, rooted in the Judo-Greco-Roman world. It is the Judo-Greco-Roman world. It is the mind of antiquity personified: truly adult. So its machine - limitation is somewhat offset by its grounding in practical experienc",
      "matched_alias": "Judo",
      "term_id": "TERM_judo",
      "term_name": "Judo",
      "term_slug": "judo"
    }
